    <p>
      My main focus right now is helping developers navigate the rapidly changing landscape of AI and machine learning. I believe that understanding these technologies will be crucial for career growth in the coming years.
    </p>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Personal</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Reading more fiction to balance out technical content</li>
      <li>Working on maintaining a healthy work-life balance</li>
      <li>Exploring hiking trails in my area</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Work</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Working as a Director of Developer Relations</li>
      <li>Creating content about developer advocacy, AI engineering, and career growth</li>
      <li>Exploring new ways to help developers level up their careers</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Learning</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Diving deeper into AI engineering and prompt engineering</li>
      <li>Improving my technical writing skills</li>
